milestones.description: P.N.G.'s 58-run win against Hong Kong is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 26-run win against U.A.E.

Mahuru Dai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (18) for PNG, going past Assad Vala
